foursquare API

To Begin:
	1) Make an account with foursquare
	2) Go to https://foursquare.com/oauth/ to register your API and get an ID and a client secret.
		-These will be needed when you try to query for data
	3) Once you query, you will be returned a json encoded object which will later needed to be decoded

There are also step by step instructions for dealing with OAuth : https://developer.foursquare.com/overview/auth

There documentation page details your query options and ways to handle foursquare accounts: https://developer.foursquare.com/docs/

Great for:

RPG's, location based apps, and many more!
